    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 prose dark:prose-invert">
      <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
      <p><em>Last updated: February 2026</em></p>

      <h2>Acceptance</h2>
      <p>By accessing PlainRecalls, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the site.</p>

